                    <span>If you are interested or involved in any way in both C/C++ development and cryptography, this book is a must.<BR>It contains all the bases and details of the most important algorithms, RSA and Rijndael:<P>- If you need mathematical information about cryptography everything is clearly explained.<BR>- If (like me)you want to experiment with practical cryptography, you will be using the RSA routines in minutes, on both VC++ or Linux. <P>The code is simple, clear, compact. Great book !</span>
                  
              
